    "The theme \"The Red Queen's Race\" is a reference to Lewis Carroll's, \"Through the Looking Glass\" (1872), in which the Red Queen tells Alice that in the new land she finds herself in, she must run as fast as she can just to stay in the same place (42)."
  ]
